Adventuring guild chest
Type: Container

This sturdy chest has the symbol of Adventurers' Guild on it.

Adventuring guild chest is an openable treasury item. It can be purchased from the Adventurers' Guild Buildings.

Loot Tables

These are the sub-tables for the various materials, coins, and items that can come from these chests.

These treasury items take 4 independent loot rolls when they are opened.
